summary: LETTER FROM MR. LUFF MANGER OF WHITEMAN INDUSTRIES OPPOSSING THOSE PROVISIONS OF EARLY WARNING REPORTING (EWR) REGULATION THAT REQUIRE MANUFACTURERS THAT PRODUCE OVER 500 SMALL-TO-MEDIUM TRAILERS(THOSE WITH VEHICLE WEIGHT RATING, GVWR OF UNDER 26000 POUNDS TO SUBMIT EARLY WARNING SYSTEM REPORTS TO NHTSA. SUCH REPORTS WOULD PUT HIM AND MANY OF HIS COLLEAGUES OUT OF BUSINESS. *AK
